PBFT engine image (*sawtooth-pbft-engine*) with "*chime*" tag does value the "*--storage-location*" option and uses "*memory*" always even with "*disk+/var/lib/sawtooth/sawtooth.data*" where */var/lib/sawtooth/* directory is present.

The above approach works with image having "*nightly*" tag.

